org.midica.file

Class CommandOption

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.midica.file.CommandOption

  • public class CommandOption
extends java.lang.Object

    Objects of this class represent a MidicaPL command option. It can be:

    • a channel option
    • an option for an INCLUDE command
    • an option for an opening or closing brace of a nestable block
